snippet.title: [ArcheWorld] Development Sneak Peek: Archeum production and enhancement
snippet.description:
Hello, Archeans!

We are glad to show you another in-game footage about gear development with Archeum and Labor, which are important materials in ArcheWorld. In this Sneak Peek, you can see how to produce Labor Potion and Archeum, and the process of gear development with acquired Archeum and Labor. I hope you enjoy the video and please look forward to more Sneak Peeks in the following weeks!

Thank you.
*The video was taken in a development stage, and some changes may occur.
